            <li>What you (do) ______ now? - I (do) ______ my homework.</li>
        </ol>
        
        <p><strong>BÀI 2:</strong> Viết câu so sánh hơn và so sánh nhất:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>This book is (interesting) ______ than that one.</li>
            <li>This is (good) ______ movie I've ever seen.</li>
            <li>My bag is (heavy) ______ than yours.</li>
        </ol>
        
